:39.000Z","msg":"建制狗令地球污染更嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ccfeda3cc347a1f990d5f1d7cec6cc2574fa2ab","tid":1670194,"uid":63543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:23:41.000Z","msg":"唔差在講埋反修例導致支那豬價急升"},{"pid":"9bdce514e34969409f8c351ac0c1a5dae291028d","tid":1670194,"uid":135409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:24:43.000Z","msg":"嘩屌， 咁撚無恥<br />\n一早已經無乜人用啦<br />\n最好攤開晒數據同日子出來講"},{"pid":"757eaf4c5beb53c97bb4596c669c7aa5a2f726e3","tid":1670194,"uid":178807,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/45wniYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F45wniYa.jpg&h=40a08cbc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c48a9b679b8c4e047360e7c00434d913ab21587d","tid":1670194,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:26:02.000Z","msg":"鳩鐵呢？"},{"pid":"e1ce8848eb657e1086224a43bc8bd520d02c0b68","tid":1670194,"uid":289751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:26:34.000Z","msg":"反修例引發中國豬瘟"},{"pid":"2cff01a386056bbd0a7265e491f622d2a599e778","tid":1670194,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:29:09.000Z","msg":"即係入晒淋病數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaaaa5d1e5c352a6ab292afe46eeceb10c9383b9","tid":1670194,"uid":70977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:30:23.000Z","msg":"一日最衰都係佔中"},{"pid":"27be0b76b00f7932c83cf14f8e4730621c2342f4","tid":1670194,"uid":310612,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:32:25.000Z","msg":"證明條橋係冇乜存在價值"},{"pid":"466d5b7ea687740c279c2d6071cdaca8270ea89a","tid":1670194,"uid":265192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:32:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">一、誠意推薦：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃</em></strong><br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2Blts4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=4c454e05\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2Blts4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=d8adb27d\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">二、什麼是遊說集團？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n遊說集團的工作，<strong><ins>是嘗試影響立法者</ins></strong>或其他持份者決定或行為，在政治角力中為服務對象<strong><ins>爭取利益</ins></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">三、為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">四、遊說集團？對家一早做緊啊！</span></span></strong><br />\n【華為被禁】華為遊說費飆60倍！原來聘用特朗普籌款人 欲說服白宮<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2479940%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2Blts4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=e9a09d74\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc</a><br />\n<br />\n董建華基金會 擲2,240萬左右美政策<br />\n大搞政治游說 否認中共代理人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2Blts4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=83befe12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&h=11b362ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175</a>"},{"pid":"33bffef80079ab14a0fabd0286b02626f6834108","tid":1670194,"uid":42135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:37:02.000Z","msg":"建制派不聽民意堅持修例致港珠澳大橋使用率不足"},{"pid":"c45b06bcab8f6ed952a30ad643d0aa5019f1d841","tid":1670194,"uid":263221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:42:05.000Z","msg":"乜都關佔中同反修例事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9d1a6c3614c5899286bff9c19e92339c8e7323","tid":1670194,"uid":1305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:43:24.000Z","msg":"養呢班弱智做議員真係浪費資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d2ca3f1fd598c07c1a873211e792d521912c51","tid":1670194,"uid":28459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T03:45:38.000Z